## Key Considerations for International Partnerships

When evaluating international academic partnerships, institutions should consider whether partner universities have:

1. Gender equity in faculty representation
2. Independent reporting systems for sexual violence
3. Clear boundaries between academic and commercial entities
4. Transparent data on sexual violence complaints and institutional responses
5. Mechanisms to protect student rights and safety

